er =E2=80=9Csenior advisor=E2=80=9D whose title fails to capture his unprec=
edented remit. While the president=E2=80=99s approval rating has softened t=
o 44 percent, according to a new Reuters/Ipsos <a href=3D"https://email.puc=
k.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dWSmt0YUFhR3poNXM3VzYx=
